---
title: Black Bean Chilli & Garlic Brown Rice Bowl with Cucumber & Radish Salsa
description: Say hello to the king of veggie bowls! There's nutrient-packed black beans that are wholesome and filling, garlic brown rice and
a rainbow of veggies, plus a radish salsa, we bow before the might of this dish.
